      "position": 2,
      "content": "AP Exam - Satisfy Course Requirement Section Economics: Macroeconomics Exam Minimum score of 3 satisfies ECON 2 Economics: Microeconomics Exam Minimum score of 3 satisfies ECON 3 Mathematics: AB Exam or AB Subscore from BC Exam Minimum score of 3 satisfies MATH 9A or MATH 7A Mathematics: BC Exam Minimum score of 3 satisfies MATH 9A and MATH 9B or MATH 7A and MATH 7B Minimum score of 4 satisfies MATH 9A, MATH 9B, MATH 9C or MATH 7A, MATH 7B, MATH 9C",
      "contentHtml": "<p><strong><u>AP Exam - Satisfy Course Requirement Section </u></strong></p><p><strong>Economics: Macroeconomics Exam </strong></p><p>Minimum score of 3 satisfies ECON 2</p><p><strong>Economics: Microeconomics Exam </strong></p><p>Minimum score of 3 satisfies ECON 3</p><p><strong>Mathematics: AB Exam or AB Subscore from BC Exam </strong></p><p>Minimum score of 3 satisfies MATH 9A <strong><u>or</u></strong> MATH 7A</p><p><strong>Mathematics: BC Exam </strong></p><p>Minimum score of 3 satisfies MATH 9A and MATH 9B <strong><u>or</u></strong> MATH 7A and MATH 7B</p><p>Minimum score of 4 satisfies MATH 9A, MATH 9B, MATH 9C <strong><u>or </u></strong>MATH 7A, MATH 7B, MATH 9C</p><p><br></p>"
